uestion thinks they can get away with it (I wonder how many people actually go through the trouble of going to the ADEA).<br /><br />Incidentally, <a href="http://gamasutra.com/view/news/238236/Im_still_creative__Game_industry_vets_rally_against_ageism.php" class="postlink">this is relevant</a>.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4526">Sik</a> — Tue Mar 17, 2015 3:36 am</p><hr />
